p;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cba2c0dd5e_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>ng ven bin</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><br /></em></p>\r\n<h2>ng bng Di&ecirc;n Kh&aacute;nh - Nha Trang</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />Nha Trang nm  ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng ng bng Di&ecirc;n Kh&aacute;nh - Nha Trang. Mt ng bng c bi lp bi s&ocirc;ng C&aacute;i Nha Trang c&oacute; din t&iacute;ch gn 300 km&sup2;, a h&igrave;nh &ograve;ng bng b ph&acirc;n h&oacute;a mnh:<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * phn ph&iacute;a T&acirc;y dc s&ocirc;ng Ch&ograve; t Kh&aacute;nh B&igrave;nh n Di&ecirc;n ng b b&oacute;c m&ograve;n,  cao tuyt i khong 10-20 m<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * phn ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng l&agrave; a h&igrave;nh t&iacute;ch t  cao tuyt i di 10m, b mt a h&igrave;nh b ph&acirc;n ct mnh bi c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng chy.</p>', '', '', '15:39:41', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (60, 16, 13, 'Vnh H Long', '', 'vinh-ha-long', '<p>Vnh H Long (vnh nc ni rng &aacute;p xung) l&agrave; mt vnh nh thuc phn b T&acirc;y vnh Bc B ti khu vc bin &ocirc;ng Bc Vit Nam, bao gm v&ugrave;ng bin o thuc th&agrave;nh ph H Long, th x&atilde; Cm Ph v&agrave; mt phn ca huyn o V&acirc;n n.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">L&agrave; trung t&acirc;m ca mt khu vc rng ln c&oacute; nhng yu t &iacute;t nhiu tng ng v a cht, a mo, cnh quan, kh&iacute; hu v&agrave; vn h&oacute;a, vi vnh B&aacute;i T Long ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng Bc v&agrave; qun o C&aacute;t B&agrave; ph&iacute;a T&acirc;y Nam, vnh H Long gii hn trong din t&iacute;ch khong 1.553km&sup2; bao gm 1.960 h&ograve;n o ln nh, phn ln l&agrave; o &aacute; v&ocirc;i, trong &oacute; v&ugrave;ng l&otilde;i ca Vnh c&oacute; din t&iacute;ch 334km&sup2; qun t d&agrave;y c 775 h&ograve;n o[. Lch s kin to a cht &aacute; v&ocirc;i ca Vnh &atilde; tri qua khong 500 triu nm vi nhng ho&agrave;n cnh c a l&yacute; rt kh&aacute;c nhau; v&agrave; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh tin h&oacute;a carxt y  tri qua tr&ecirc;n 20 triu nm vi s kt hp c&aacute;c yu t nh tng &aacute; v&ocirc;i d&agrave;y, kh&iacute; hu n&oacute;ng m v&agrave; tin tr&igrave;nh n&acirc;ng kin to chm chp tr&ecirc;n tng th S kt hp ca m&ocirc;i trng, kh&iacute; hu, a cht, a mo, &atilde; khin vnh H Long tr th&agrave;nh qun t ca a dng sinh hc bao gm h sinh th&aacute;i rng k&iacute;n thng xanh ma m nhit i v&agrave; h sinh th&aacute;i bin v&agrave; ven b vi nhiu tiu h sinh th&aacute;i. 14 lo&agrave;i thc vt c hu v&agrave; khong 60 lo&agrave;i ng vt c hu &atilde; c ph&aacute;t hin trong s h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;n ng, thc vt qun c ti Vnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb60b67f10_crop.JPG" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>H&ograve;n Trng M&aacute;i</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nhng kt qu nghi&ecirc;n cu, th&aacute;m s&aacute;t kho c hc v&agrave; vn h&oacute;a hc cho thy s hin din ca nhng c d&acirc;n tin s tr&ecirc;n v&ugrave;ng vnh H Long t kh&aacute; sm, &atilde; to lp nhng h&igrave;nh th&aacute;i vn h&oacute;a c i tip ni nhau bao gm vn h&oacute;a Soi Nh trong khong 18.000-7.000 nm trc C&ocirc;ng Nguy&ecirc;n, vn h&oacute;a C&aacute;i B&egrave;o trong 7.000-5.000 nm trc C&ocirc;ng Nguy&ecirc;n v&agrave; vn h&oacute;a H Long c&aacute;ch ng&agrave;y nay khong t 3.500-5.000 nm. Tin tr&igrave;nh dng nc v&agrave; truyn thng gi nc ca d&acirc;n tc Vit Nam, trong sut h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh lch s, cng khng nh v tr&iacute; tin ti&ecirc;u v&agrave; v th vn h&oacute;a ca vnh H Long qua nhng a danh m&agrave; t&ecirc;n gi gn vi in t&iacute;ch c&ograve;n lu truyn n nay, nh n&uacute;i B&agrave;i Th, hang u G, B&atilde;i Ch&aacute;yv.v. Hin nay, vnh H Long l&agrave; mt khu vc ph&aacute;t trin nng ng nh nhng iu kin v&agrave; li th sn c&oacute; nh c&oacute; mt tim nng ln v du lch, nghi&ecirc;n cu khoa hc, nu&ocirc;i trng, &aacute;nh bt thy sn, giao th&ocirc;ng thy i vi khu vc v&ugrave;ng bin &ocirc;ng Bc Vit Nam n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng v&agrave; min Bc Vit Nam n&oacute;i chung.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb60a1bf5b_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>ng Thien Cung </em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br /><br />T hn 500 nm v trc trong b&agrave;i th L nhp V&acirc;n n, Nguyn Tr&atilde;i &atilde; ln u ti&ecirc;n ca ngi vnh H Long l&agrave; "k quan &aacute; dng gia tri cao". Nm 1962 B Vn h&oacute;a-Th&ocirc;ng tin Vit Nam &atilde; xp hng vnh H Long l&agrave; di t&iacute;ch danh thng cp quc gia ng thi quy hoch v&ugrave;ng bo v. Nm 1994 v&ugrave;ng l&otilde;i ca vnh H Long c UNESCO c&ocirc;ng nhn l&agrave; Di sn Thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n Th gii vi gi&aacute; tr thm m (ti&ecirc;u chun vii), v&agrave; c t&aacute;i c&ocirc;ng nhn ln th 2 vi gi&aacute; tr ngoi hng to&agrave;n cu v a cht-a mo (ti&ecirc;u chun viii) v&agrave;o nm 2000. C&ugrave;ng vi vnh Nha Trang ca Vit Nam, vnh H Long l&agrave; mt trong s 29 vnh c C&acirc;u lc b nhng vnh p nht th gii xp hng v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh thc c&ocirc;ng nhn v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 7 nm 2003.<br /><br />Vnh H Long c&ugrave;ng vi o C&aacute;t B&agrave; to th&agrave;nh 1 trong 21 khu du lch quc gia Vit Nam</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:39:57', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (61, 10, 14, 'Cha Mt Ct', '', 'chua-mot-cot', '<p>Ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct hay Ch&ugrave;a Mt (gi theo H&aacute;n-Vit l&agrave; Nht Tr th&aacute;p ), c&ograve;n c&oacute; t&ecirc;n kh&aacute;c l&agrave; Di&ecirc;n Hu t () hoc Li&ecirc;n Hoa &agrave;i (, "&agrave;i hoa sen"), l&agrave; mt ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a nm gia l&ograve;ng th &ocirc; H&agrave; Ni. &acirc;y l&agrave; ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a c&oacute; kin tr&uacute;c c &aacute;o  Vit Nam.</p>', '<h2><span id="L.E1.BB.8Bch_s.E1.BB.AD" class="mw-headline">Lch s</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ch&ugrave;a Di&ecirc;n Hu c vua L&yacute; Th&aacute;i T&ocirc;ng cho khi c&ocirc;ng x&acirc;y dng v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a &ocirc;ng th&aacute;ng mi (&acirc;m lch) nm K Su 1049, ni&ecirc;n hiu Thi&ecirc;n Cm Th&aacute;nh V&otilde; th nht.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nhng theo cun H&agrave; Ni-di t&iacute;ch lch s v&agrave; danh thng, nh&oacute;m c&aacute;c nh&agrave; s hc inh Xu&acirc;n L&acirc;m, Do&atilde;n oan Trinh, Dng Trung Quc, Nguyn Quang &Acirc;n, Nguyn Thanh Mai, &agrave;m T&aacute;i Hng tin h&agrave;nh nghi&ecirc;n cu vn bia dng ti ch&ugrave;a nm Cnh Tr th 3 (1665), i vua L&ecirc; Huyn T&ocirc;ng, do T Khu L&ecirc; Tt t khc ghi, th&igrave; thy rng: ti v tr&iacute; ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct ng&agrave;y nay, v&agrave;o thi nh&agrave; ng (nm H&agrave;m Thng th nht) mt ct &aacute; tr&ecirc;n c&oacute; ng&ocirc;i lu ngc (vi tng Pht Quan &Acirc;m  trong) &atilde; c dng gia mt h nc vu&ocirc;ng. Vua L&yacute; Th&aacute;i T&ocirc;ng thng n cu nguyn, c ho&agrave;ng t ni d&otilde;i, lin tu sa li th&agrave;nh ch&ugrave;a, x&acirc;y th&ecirc;m mt ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a b&ecirc;n cnh ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct (c&aacute;ch 10 m v ph&iacute;a T&acirc;y Nam) v&agrave; t t&ecirc;n c qun th ch&ugrave;a n&agrave;y l&agrave; Di&ecirc;n Hu t (vi ngha l&agrave; "ph&uacute;c l&agrave;nh d&agrave;i l&acirc;u").</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nm 1954, qu&acirc;n i Vin chinh Ph&aacute;p trc khi r&uacute;t khi H&agrave; Ni &atilde; cho t m&igrave;m ph&aacute; ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct. B&aacute;o Tia s&aacute;ng ng&agrave;y 10-9-1954 a tin "..., ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct di t&iacute;ch lit hng ca H&agrave; Th&agrave;nh &atilde; sp  sau mt ting long tri l t..." Sau khi tip qun th &ocirc;, B Vn h&oacute;a Vit Nam D&acirc;n ch Cng h&ograve;a &atilde; tin h&agrave;nh tr&ugrave;ng tu ln ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct v&agrave; ch&ugrave;a Di&ecirc;n Hu, x&acirc;y dng li ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct theo kin tr&uacute;c c.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct ch c&oacute; mt gian nm tr&ecirc;n mt ct &aacute;  gia h Linh Chiu nh c&oacute; trng hoa sen. Truyn thuyt k li rng, ch&ugrave;a c x&acirc;y dng theo gic m ca vua L&yacute; Th&aacute;i T&ocirc;ng (1028-1054) v&agrave; theo gi &yacute; thit k ca nh&agrave; s Thin Tu. V&agrave;o nm 1049, vua &atilde; m thy c Pht b&agrave; Quan &Acirc;m ngi tr&ecirc;n t&ograve;a sen dt vua l&ecirc;n to&agrave;. Khi tnh dy, nh&agrave; vua k chuyn &oacute; li vi b&agrave;y t&ocirc;i v&agrave; c nh&agrave; s Thin Tu khuy&ecirc;n dng ch&ugrave;a, dng ct &aacute; nh trong chi&ecirc;m bao, l&agrave;m to&agrave; sen ca Pht b&agrave; Quan &Acirc;m t tr&ecirc;n ct nh &atilde; thy trong mng v&agrave; cho c&aacute;c nh&agrave; s i v&ograve;ng xung quanh tng kinh cu k&eacute;o d&agrave;i s ph&ugrave; h, v&igrave; th ch&ugrave;a mang t&ecirc;n Di&ecirc;n Hu.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ca50b95de3_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct nh&igrave;n t ph&iacute;a sau</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><br /></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hng nm c n ng&agrave;y 8 th&aacute;ng 4 &Acirc;m lch, vua li ti ch&ugrave;a l&agrave;m l tm Pht. C&aacute;c nh&agrave; s v&agrave; nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n khp Kinh th&agrave;nh Thng Long c&ugrave;ng d l. Sau l tm Pht l&agrave; l ph&oacute;ng sinh, vua ng tr&ecirc;n mt &agrave;i cao trc ch&ugrave;a th mt con chim bay i, ri nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c&ugrave;ng tung chim bay theo trong ting reo vui ca mt ng&agrave;y hi ln.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">n nm 1105, vua L&yacute; Nh&acirc;n T&ocirc;ng cho sa ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a v&agrave; cho dng trc s&acirc;n hai th&aacute;p lp s trng. Nm 1108, Nguy&ecirc;n phi  Lan sai b&agrave;y t&ocirc;i &uacute;c mt c&aacute;i chu&ocirc;ng rt to, nng den mt vn hai ngh&igrave;n c&acirc;n, t t&ecirc;n l&agrave; "Gi&aacute;c th chung" (Qu chu&ocirc;ng thc tnh ngi i). &acirc;y c xem l&agrave; mt trong t i kh&iacute; - bn c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ln ca Vit Nam thi &oacute; - l&agrave;: th&aacute;p B&aacute;o Thi&ecirc;n, chu&ocirc;ng Quy in, vc Ph Minh v&agrave; tng Qunh L&acirc;m. "Gi&aacute;c th chung" &uacute;c xong nng qu&aacute; kh&ocirc;ng treo l&ecirc;n c,  di mt t th&igrave; &aacute;nh kh&ocirc;ng k&ecirc;u. Ngi ta &agrave;nh b chu&ocirc;ng xung mt tha rung s&acirc;u b&ecirc;n ch&ugrave;a Nht Tr, rung n&agrave;y c&oacute; nhiu r&ugrave;a, do &oacute; c&oacute; t&ecirc;n la Quy in chu&ocirc;ng (chu&ocirc;ng rung r&ugrave;a). n th k 15, gic Minh x&acirc;m lc, chim th&agrave;nh &ocirc;ng Quan (H&agrave; Ni). Nm 1426 L&ecirc; Li em ngha qu&acirc;n Lam Sn ra &aacute;nh, v&acirc;y th&agrave;nh rt gp. Qu&acirc;n Minh thiu thn v kh&iacute; n dc, tng Minh l&agrave; Vng Th&ocirc;ng b&egrave;n sai ngi em ph&aacute; chu&ocirc;ng Quy in ly ng. Qu&acirc;n Minh thua trn, nhng chu&ocirc;ng Quy in th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n na.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ca50c97cd8_crop.JPG" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">To&agrave;n cnh ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vn bia th&aacute;p S&ugrave;ng thin di&ecirc;n linh (ch&ugrave;a i, H&agrave; Nam), nm 1121 vit: "Do l&ograve;ng s&ugrave;ng k&iacute;nh c Pht v&agrave; dc l&ograve;ng m o nh&acirc;n qu (o Pht) n&ecirc;n hng v vn T&acirc;y Cm ni danh (Ng&ocirc;i vn  ph&iacute;a t&acirc;y cm th&agrave;nh Thng Long i L&yacute;) m&agrave; x&acirc;y ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a s&aacute;ng Di&ecirc;n Hu theo du vt ch  c, c&ugrave;ng vi &yacute; mu mi ca nh&agrave; vua (&yacute; n&oacute;i: theo du vt l li x&acirc;y dng ch&ugrave;a i L&yacute; Th&aacute;nh T&ocirc;ng, c&oacute; th&ecirc;m &yacute; mi ca L&yacute; Nh&acirc;n T&ocirc;ng m&agrave; cha li ch&ugrave;a p hn trc)".</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">n thi nh&agrave; Trn, ch&ugrave;a &atilde; kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave; ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a nh&agrave; L&yacute; na v&igrave; s&aacute;ch c &atilde; ghi: Nm 1249, "...m&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n, th&aacute;ng gi&ecirc;ng, sa li ch&ugrave;a Di&ecirc;n Hu, xung chiu vn l&agrave;m  nn c...".<br /><br />Ch&ugrave;a Mt Ct c tr&ugrave;ng tu v&agrave;o khong nhng nm 1840-1850 v&agrave; v&agrave;o nm 1922. &agrave;i Li&ecirc;n Hoa ch&uacute;ng ta thy hin nay c sa cha li nm 1955 do kin-tr&uacute;c-s Nguyn B&aacute; Lng m-nhim.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:40:22', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (62, 12, 20, 'Bnh chng', '', 'banh-chung', '<p>B&aacute;nh chng l&agrave; mt loi b&aacute;nh truyn thng ca d&acirc;n tc Vit nhm th hin l&ograve;ng bit n ca con ch&aacute;u i vi cha &ocirc;ng v&agrave; t tri x s. Nguy&ecirc;n liu l&agrave;m b&aacute;nh bao gm go np, u xanh, tht ln, l&aacute; dong v&agrave; b&aacute;nh thng c l&agrave;m v&agrave;o c&aacute;c dp Tt c truyn ca d&acirc;n tc Vit, cng nh ng&agrave;y gi t H&ugrave;ng Vng) (m&ugrave;ng 10 th&aacute;ng 3 &acirc;m lch).</p>', '<h2><span id="S.E1.BB.B1_t.C3.ADch" class="mw-headline">S t&iacute;ch</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">L&agrave; loi b&aacute;nh duy nht c&oacute; lch s l&acirc;u i trong m thc truyn thng Vit Nam c&ograve;n c s s&aacute;ch nhc li, b&aacute;nh chng c&oacute; v tr&iacute; c bit trong t&acirc;m thc ca cng ng ngi Vit v&agrave; ngun gc ca n&oacute; c&oacute; th truy nguy&ecirc;n v truyn thuyt li&ecirc;n quan n ho&agrave;ng t Lang Li&ecirc;u v&agrave;o i vua H&ugrave;ng th 6. S t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n mun. nhc nh con ch&aacute;u v truyn thng ca d&acirc;n tc; l&agrave; li gii th&iacute;ch &yacute; ngha cng nh ngun ci ca ca B&aacute;nh Chng, B&aacute;nh Giy trong vn h&oacute;a, ng thi nhn mnh tm quan trng ca c&acirc;y l&uacute;a v&agrave; thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n trong nn vn ho&aacute; l&uacute;a nc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cac4720ab1_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Mt chic b&aacute;nh chng vu&ocirc;ng v&agrave; mt chic b&aacute;nh chng t&agrave;y va c g&oacute;i</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span id="Quan_ni.E1.BB.87m_truy.E1.BB.81n_th.E1.BB.91ng" class="mw-headline">Quan nim truyn thng</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo quan nim ph bin hin nay, c&ugrave;ng vi b&aacute;nh giy, b&aacute;nh chng tng trng cho quan nim v v tr ca ngi Vit xa. B&aacute;nh c&oacute; m&agrave;u xanh l&aacute; c&acirc;y, h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng, c coi l&agrave; c trng cho t trong t&iacute;n ngng ca ngi Vit c v&agrave; c&aacute;c d&acirc;n tc kh&aacute;c trong khu vc ch&acirc;u &Aacute;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, theo Gi&aacute;o s Trn Quc Vng, b&aacute;nh chng nguy&ecirc;n thy c&oacute; h&igrave;nh tr&ograve;n v&agrave; d&agrave;i, ging nh b&aacute;nh t&eacute;t, [ng thi b&aacute;nh chng v&agrave; b&aacute;nh giy tng trng cho nam v&agrave; n trong t&iacute;n ngng phn thc Vit Nam. B&aacute;nh t&eacute;t, thay th v tr&iacute; ca b&aacute;nh chng v&agrave;o c&aacute;c dp Tt trong cng ng ngi Vit  min nam Vit Nam, theo Trn Quc Vng l&agrave; dng nguy&ecirc;n thy ca b&aacute;nh chng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cac46114ad_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">B&aacute;nh chng v&agrave; gi&ograve; la</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">G&oacute;i v&agrave; nu b&aacute;nh chng, ngi canh ni b&aacute;nh chng tr&ecirc;n bp la &atilde; tr th&agrave;nh mt tp qu&aacute;n, vn h&oacute;a sng trong c&aacute;c gia &igrave;nh ngi Vit mi dp tt n xu&acirc;n v.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:41:43', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (80, 23, 2, 'Colled cake', '', 'colled-cake', '<p style="text-align: justify;">B&aacute;nh cun (literally "rolled cake") is a dish from northern Vietnam.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">It is a cr&ecirc;pe-like roll made from a thin, wide sheet of rice flour filled with ground pork, minced wood ear mushroom, and other ingredients. Sides for this dish usually consist of ch la (Vietnamese pork sausage) and bean sprouts, with the dipping sauce called nc chm. Sometimes, a drop of c&agrave; cung, which is the essence of a giant water bug, Lethocerus indicus, is added to the nc chm for extra flavor, although this ingredient is scarce and quite expensive.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cc37ba9053_small.jpg" alt="" width="207" height="155" /> <img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cc37d048e1_small.JPG" alt="" width="207" height="155" /> <img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cc37e5c955_small.jpg" alt="" width="235" height="153" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Unlike shahe fen, the rice sheet in b&aacute;nh cun is extremely thin and delicate. It is a light dish, and is generally eaten for breakfast everywhere in Vietnam. A different version of b&aacute;nh cun, called b&aacute;nh cun Thanh Tr&igrave; and b&aacute;nh cun l&agrave;ng K&ecirc;nh, may be found in Thanh Tr&igrave;, a southern district of Hanoi and K&ecirc;nh village of Nam nh, an ancient village in the centre of Nam nh city.B&aacute;nh cun Thanh Tr&igrave; or B&aacute;nh cun l&agrave;ng K&ecirc;nh are not rolls, but just rice sheets eaten with ch la, fried shallots, or prawns; see the article B&aacute;nh cun in the Vietnamese Wikipedia.<br /><br />A similar Chinese dish is the Cantonese dish coeng4 fan2 (; pinyin: ch&aacute;ngfn), usually translated into English as "steamed rice roll" or "rice noodle roll," which is a form of dim sum.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '16:03:02', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (63, 12, 20, 'Bnh chng', '', 'banh-chung', '<p>B&aacute;nh chng l&agrave; mt loi b&aacute;nh truyn thng ca d&acirc;n tc Vit nhm th hin l&ograve;ng bit n ca con ch&aacute;u i vi cha &ocirc;ng v&agrave; t tri x s. Nguy&ecirc;n liu l&agrave;m b&aacute;nh bao gm go np, u xanh, tht ln, l&aacute; dong v&agrave; b&aacute;nh thng c l&agrave;m v&agrave;o c&aacute;c dp Tt c truyn ca d&acirc;n tc Vit, cng nh ng&agrave;y gi t H&ugrave;ng Vng) (m&ugrave;ng 10 th&aacute;ng 3 &acirc;m lch).</p>', '<h2><span id="S.E1.BB.B1_t.C3.ADch" class="mw-headline">S t&iacute;ch</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">L&agrave; loi b&aacute;nh duy nht c&oacute; lch s l&acirc;u i trong m thc truyn thng Vit Nam c&ograve;n c s s&aacute;ch nhc li, b&aacute;nh chng c&oacute; v tr&iacute; c bit trong t&acirc;m thc ca cng ng ngi Vit v&agrave; ngun gc ca n&oacute; c&oacute; th truy nguy&ecirc;n v truyn thuyt li&ecirc;n quan n ho&agrave;ng t Lang Li&ecirc;u v&agrave;o i vua H&ugrave;ng th 6. S t&iacute;ch tr&ecirc;n mun. nhc nh con ch&aacute;u v truyn thng ca d&acirc;n tc; l&agrave; li gii th&iacute;ch &yacute; ngha cng nh ngun ci ca ca B&aacute;nh Chng, B&aacute;nh Giy trong vn h&oacute;a, ng thi nhn mnh tm quan trng ca c&acirc;y l&uacute;a v&agrave; thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n trong nn vn ho&aacute; l&uacute;a nc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cac4720ab1_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Mt chic b&aacute;nh chng vu&ocirc;ng v&agrave; mt chic b&aacute;nh chng t&agrave;y va c g&oacute;i</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span id="Quan_ni.E1.BB.87m_truy.E1.BB.81n_th.E1.BB.91ng" class="mw-headline">Quan nim truyn thng</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo quan nim ph bin hin nay, c&ugrave;ng vi b&aacute;nh giy, b&aacute;nh chng tng trng cho quan nim v v tr ca ngi Vit xa. B&aacute;nh c&oacute; m&agrave;u xanh l&aacute; c&acirc;y, h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng, c coi l&agrave; c trng cho t trong t&iacute;n ngng ca ngi Vit c v&agrave; c&aacute;c d&acirc;n tc kh&aacute;c trong khu vc ch&acirc;u &Aacute;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, theo Gi&aacute;o s Trn Quc Vng, b&aacute;nh chng nguy&ecirc;n thy c&oacute; h&igrave;nh tr&ograve;n v&agrave; d&agrave;i, ging nh b&aacute;nh t&eacute;t, [ng thi b&aacute;nh chng v&agrave; b&aacute;nh giy tng trng cho nam v&agrave; n trong t&iacute;n ngng phn thc Vit Nam. B&aacute;nh t&eacute;t, thay th v tr&iacute; ca b&aacute;nh chng v&agrave;o c&aacute;c dp Tt trong cng ng ngi Vit  min nam Vit Nam, theo Trn Quc Vng l&agrave; dng nguy&ecirc;n thy ca b&aacute;nh chng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cac46114ad_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">B&aacute;nh chng v&agrave; gi&ograve; la</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">G&oacute;i v&agrave; nu b&aacute;nh chng, ngi canh ni b&aacute;nh chng tr&ecirc;n bp la &atilde; tr th&agrave;nh mt tp qu&aacute;n, vn h&oacute;a sng trong c&aacute;c gia &igrave;nh ngi Vit mi dp tt n xu&acirc;n v.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:41:43', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (64, 14, 17, 'm thc Vit Nam', '', 'am-thuc-viet-nam', '<p>m thc Vit Nam l&agrave; c&aacute;ch gi ca phng thc ch bin m&oacute;n n, nguy&ecirc;n l&yacute; phi trn gia v v&agrave; nhng th&oacute;i quen n ung n&oacute;i chung ca mi ngi Vit tr&ecirc;n t nc Vit Nam. Tuy hu nh c&oacute; &iacute;t nhiu c&oacute; s kh&aacute;c bit, m thc Vit Nam vn bao h&agrave;m &yacute; ngha kh&aacute;i qu&aacute;t nht  ch tt c nhng m&oacute;n n ph bin trong cng ng c&aacute;c d&acirc;n tc thiu s nhng &atilde; tng i ph th&ocirc;ng trong cng ng ngi Vit.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb06864644_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>H tiu<br /></em></p>\r\n<h3><span id="B.E1.BB.AFa_.C4.83n_gia_.C4.91.C3.ACnh_Vi.E1.BB.87t_Nam_truy.E1.BB.81n_th.E1.BB.91ng" class="mw-headline">Ba n gia &igrave;nh Vit Nam truyn thng</span></h3>\r\n<p>Ngi Vit thng n ph v&agrave;o bui s&aacute;ng vi c&aacute;c thc qu&agrave; vt (nh c&aacute;c loi b&aacute;nh, x&ocirc;i, ch&aacute;o, ph, b&uacute;n). Mt ba n ch&iacute;nh, c trng ca mt gia &igrave;nh Vit Nam din ra v&agrave;o bui tra v&agrave;/hoc bui ti, th&ocirc;ng thng l&agrave; khi gia &igrave;nh &atilde; t hp &ocirc;ng . Ba n ch&iacute;nh ca ngi Vit thng bao gm mt m&oacute;n ch lc (cm), mt m&oacute;n gia v (nc chm) v&agrave; ba m&oacute;n n c bn  cht v&agrave; c&acirc;n bng &acirc;m dng:<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Mt ni cm chung cho c gia &igrave;nh (mi ngi c&oacute; mt c&aacute;i b&aacute;t nh v&agrave; &ocirc;i a ca ri&ecirc;ng m&igrave;nh)<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Mt b&aacute;t nh ng nc chm (nc mm, tng hoc x&igrave; du) c gia &igrave;nh d&ugrave;ng chung.<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Mt m&oacute;n mn c&oacute; cht m ng vt v&agrave; cht b&eacute;o c luc, r&aacute;n hoc kho nh tht, c&aacute;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Mt m&oacute;n rau luc hoc x&agrave;o, hoc rau thm, rau sng, da mui<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Mt m&oacute;n canh c&oacute; th m &agrave;, cu k nhng cng kh&ocirc;ng him khi ch n gin l&agrave; mt b&aacute;t nc luc rau<br /><br />Hin nay, do i sng c n&acirc;ng cao hn, c cu ba n ch&iacute;nh ca ngi Vit hin cng &atilde; ci thin &aacute;ng k theo hng gia tng c&aacute;c m&oacute;n mn nhiu dinh dng s dng nguy&ecirc;n liu ng vt. B&ecirc;n cnh xu hng mt s v&ugrave;ng min (nht l&agrave; nhng v&ugrave;ng th&ocirc;n qu&ecirc;) vn c&ograve;n b&agrave;y v c&agrave;ng nhiu m&oacute;n tr&ecirc;n m&acirc;m c&agrave;ng tt, nhiu gia &igrave;nh th&agrave;nh th li ch&uacute; trng xu hng tinh gin bng c&aacute;ch ch nu mt m&oacute;n trng t&acirc;m c&oacute;  cht m v&agrave; c&aacute;c loi rau b&agrave;y l&ecirc;n m&acirc;m, n k&egrave;m vi c&aacute;c loi rau da lt vt kh&aacute;c. Mt s gia &igrave;nh l&agrave;m c&aacute;c m&oacute;n n c bit nh&acirc;n ng&agrave;y ch nht rnh ri, nhng m&oacute;n cu k m&agrave; ng&agrave;y thng &iacute;t c&oacute; thi gian  l&agrave;m. B&aacute;t nc chm "cng ng" nay cng dn c nhiu gia &igrave;nh, hoc c&aacute;c nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng cu k san ri&ecirc;ng ra b&aacute;t cho tng ngi  hp v sinh hn, v&agrave; c&oacute; nhiu loi nc chm kh&aacute;c nhau t&ugrave;y theo trong ba c&oacute; loi  n g&igrave;.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>C b&agrave;n</h3>\r\n<p>C b&agrave;n thng s dng nhiu m&oacute;n n trong &oacute; nhn mnh c bit c&aacute;c m&oacute;n mn d&ugrave;ng nguy&ecirc;n liu ng vt, loi tr tt c nhng m&oacute;n n ng&agrave;y thng nh rau luc, da c&agrave; v.v.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>C c&uacute;ng t ti&ecirc;n</h3>\r\n<p>C&uacute;ng t ti&ecirc;n (ng&agrave;y gi chp, ng&agrave;y tt c truyn) thng s dng x&ocirc;i u xanh, x&ocirc;i gc vi g&agrave; luc nguy&ecirc;n con hoc ch&acirc;n gi&ograve;. C&uacute;ng ngi mi mt ch d&ugrave;ng x&ocirc;i trng v&agrave; mt qu trng luc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>C Tt<span id="B.E1.BB.AFa_.C4.83n_gia_.C4.91.C3.ACnh_Vi.E1.BB.87t_Nam_truy.E1.BB.81n_th.E1.BB.91ng" class="mw-headline"> <br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>C tt truyn thng rt cu k, m&acirc;m c c bn thng l&agrave; 5 b&aacute;t: b&oacute;ng, min, mng, mc, chim hoc g&agrave; tn v&agrave; 5 a: gi&ograve;, ch, g&agrave; hoc vt luc, nm, x&agrave;o. Ng&agrave;y nay m&acirc;m c tt &atilde; c&oacute; nhiu thay i v thc n theo xu hng tinh gin, ch&uacute; trng "chi" hn "n".</p>', '', '', '15:42:01', 1, 'admin');
