; cht b&eacute;o c luc, r&aacute;n hoc kho nh tht, c&aacute;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Mt m&oacute;n rau luc hoc x&agrave;o, hoc rau thm, rau sng, da mui<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Mt m&oacute;n canh c&oacute; th m &agrave;, cu k nhng cng kh&ocirc;ng him khi ch n gin l&agrave; mt b&aacute;t nc luc rau<br /><br />Hin nay, do i sng c n&acirc;ng cao hn, c cu ba n ch&iacute;nh ca ngi Vit hin cng &atilde; ci thin &aacute;ng k theo hng gia tng c&aacute;c m&oacute;n mn nhiu dinh dng s dng nguy&ecirc;n liu ng vt. B&ecirc;n cnh xu hng mt s v&ugrave;ng min (nht l&agrave; nhng v&ugrave;ng th&ocirc;n qu&ecirc;) vn c&ograve;n b&agrave;y v c&agrave;ng nhiu m&oacute;n tr&ecirc;n m&acirc;m c&agrave;ng tt, nhiu gia &igrave;nh th&agrave;nh th li ch&uacute; trng xu hng tinh gin bng c&aacute;ch ch nu mt m&oacute;n trng t&acirc;m c&oacute;  cht m v&agrave; c&aacute;c loi rau b&agrave;y l&ecirc;n m&acirc;m, n k&egrave;m vi c&aacute;c loi rau da lt vt kh&aacute;c. Mt s gia &igrave;nh l&agrave;m c&aacute;c m&oacute;n n c bit nh&acirc;n ng&agrave;y ch nht rnh ri, nhng m&oacute;n cu k m&agrave; ng&agrave;y thng &iacute;t c&oacute; thi gian  l&agrave;m. B&aacute;t nc chm "cng ng" nay cng dn c nhiu gia &igrave;nh, hoc c&aacute;c nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng cu k san ri&ecirc;ng ra b&aacute;t cho tng ngi  hp v sinh hn, v&agrave; c&oacute; nhiu loi nc chm kh&aacute;c nhau t&ugrave;y theo trong ba c&oacute; loi  n g&igrave;.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>C b&agrave;n</h3>\r\n<p>C b&agrave;n thng s dng nhiu m&oacute;n n trong &oacute; nhn mnh c bit c&aacute;c m&oacute;n mn d&ugrave;ng nguy&ecirc;n liu ng vt, loi tr tt c nhng m&oacute;n n ng&agrave;y thng nh rau luc, da c&agrave; v.v.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>C c&uacute;ng t ti&ecirc;n</h3>\r\n<p>C&uacute;ng t ti&ecirc;n (ng&agrave;y gi chp, ng&agrave;y tt c truyn) thng s dng x&ocirc;i u xanh, x&ocirc;i gc vi g&agrave; luc nguy&ecirc;n con hoc ch&acirc;n gi&ograve;. C&uacute;ng ngi mi mt ch d&ugrave;ng x&ocirc;i trng v&agrave; mt qu trng luc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>C Tt<span id="B.E1.BB.AFa_.C4.83n_gia_.C4.91.C3.ACnh_Vi.E1.BB.87t_Nam_truy.E1.BB.81n_th.E1.BB.91ng" class="mw-headline"> <br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>C tt truyn thng rt cu k, m&acirc;m c c bn thng l&agrave; 5 b&aacute;t: b&oacute;ng, min, mng, mc, chim hoc g&agrave; tn v&agrave; 5 a: gi&ograve;, ch, g&agrave; hoc vt luc, nm, x&agrave;o. Ng&agrave;y nay m&acirc;m c tt &atilde; c&oacute; nhiu thay i v thc n theo xu hng tinh gin, ch&uacute; trng "chi" hn "n".</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:42:49', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (67, 21, 1, 'Da Lat', '', 'da-lat', '<p>Da Lat, or Dalat, (pop. 197,000 as of 2007[update], spelled &agrave; Lt in Vietnamese) About this sound pronunciation (help&middot;info) is the capital of L&acirc;m ng Province in Vietnam.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde84daa7_crop.JPG" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Tuyn L&acirc;m Lake in the morning fog&nbsp; </em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The city is located 1,500 m (4,900 ft) above sea level on the Langbiang Plateau in the southern parts of the Central Highlands (in Vietnamese, T&acirc;y Nguy&ecirc;n). In Vietnam, &agrave; Lt is a popular tourist destination.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde95d244_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><small>Outside Da Lat Market at night</small></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&agrave; Lt''s specific sights are pine wood (forming the name: "City of thousands of pine trees") with twisting roads and tree marigold (Vietnamese: d&atilde; qu) blossom in the winter. The city''s temperate weather stands in contrast to Vietnam''s otherwise tropical climate. Mist covering the valleys almost year-round leads to its name "City of eternal spring."</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde738539_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Da Lat''s Market square at night</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&agrave; Lt is also known as an area for science research in the fields of biotechnology and nuclear physics.<br /><br />With its year-round cool weather, &agrave; Lt supplies temperate agriculture products for all over Vietnam, for example, cabbage and cauliflower. Its flower industry produces two typical flowers: hydrangea (Vietnamese: cm t&uacute; cu) and golden everlasting (Vietnamese: hoa bt t). The confectionery industry offers a wide range of mt, a kind of fruit preserve made from strawberry, mulberry, sweet potato, and rose.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:43:17', 1, 'admin');
