="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&agrave; Lt is also known as an area for science research in the fields of biotechnology and nuclear physics.<br /><br />With its year-round cool weather, &agrave; Lt supplies temperate agriculture products for all over Vietnam, for example, cabbage and cauliflower. Its flower industry produces two typical flowers: hydrangea (Vietnamese: cm t&uacute; cu) and golden everlasting (Vietnamese: hoa bt t). The confectionery industry offers a wide range of mt, a kind of fruit preserve made from strawberry, mulberry, sweet potato, and rose.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:43:17', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (69, 22, 13, ' Lt', '', 'da-lat', '<p>&agrave; Lt l&agrave; mt th&agrave;nh ph trc thuc tnh v&agrave; tnh l tnh L&acirc;m ng, nm tr&ecirc;n cao nguy&ecirc;n L&acirc;m Vi&ecirc;n,   cao 1.500 m so vi mt nc bin v&agrave; din t&iacute;ch t nhi&ecirc;n: 393,29 km&sup2;.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde84daa7_crop.JPG" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>H Tuyn L&acirc;m</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&agrave; Lt c Th tng ch&iacute;nh ph Vit Nam c&ocirc;ng nhn l&agrave; &ocirc; th loi 1 v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 24 th&aacute;ng 3 nm 2009. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt trong 6 &ocirc; th loi 1 thuc tnh.<br /><br />Vi nhiu cnh quan p, &agrave; Lt l&agrave; mt trong nhng th&agrave;nh ph du lch ni ting nht ca Vit Nam. Trong thi Ph&aacute;p thuc, t&ecirc;n ting Latin Dat Aliis Laetitiam Aliis Temperiem c&oacute; ngha l&agrave; "cho nhng ngi n&agrave;y nim vui, cho nhng ngi kh&aacute;c s m&aacute;t m"[2]. &agrave; Lt c mnh danh l&agrave;: th&agrave;nh ph hoa, th&agrave;nh ph t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u, th&agrave;nh ph m&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n, th&agrave;nh ph sng m&ugrave;.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde95d244_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><small>Ch &agrave; Lt<br /></small></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Th&agrave;nh ph &agrave; Lt nm trong cao nguy&ecirc;n Lang Biang, ph&iacute;a Bc tnh L&acirc;m ng, V ph&iacute;a Bc, &agrave; Lt gi&aacute;p vi huyn Lc Dng, v ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng v&agrave; &ocirc;ng Nam gi&aacute;p vi huyn n Dng, v ph&iacute;a T&acirc;y v&agrave; T&acirc;y Nam gi&aacute;p vi hai huyn L&acirc;m H&agrave; v&agrave; c Trng.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cbde738539_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Ch &agrave; Lt v &ecirc;m<br /></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">H&agrave;ng trm nm trc &acirc;y, &agrave; Lt l&agrave; a b&agrave;n c tr&uacute; ca ngi Lch, vn l&agrave; c d&acirc;n ca to&agrave;n b cao nguy&ecirc;n Lang Biang. &agrave; Lt c&oacute; din t&iacute;ch hn 400 km&sup2;, bao bc bi c&aacute;c nh n&uacute;i cao v&agrave; d&atilde;y n&uacute;i li&ecirc;n tip:<br /> <br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Ph&iacute;a Bc v&agrave; T&acirc;y Bc gii hn bi d&atilde;y Chormui, Y a Myut (1.816 m), T&acirc;y Bc da v&agrave;o ch&acirc;n d&atilde;y n&uacute;i Ch Yang Kae (1.921 m), thuc qun sn Lang Biang m&agrave; nh cao nht l&agrave; Ch Yang Sinh (1.408 m).<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng l&agrave; ch&acirc;n d&atilde;y n&uacute;i Bi Doup (2.278 m) dc xung cao nguy&ecirc;n Dran.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng Nam chn bi d&atilde;y Cho Proline (1.629 m).<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Ph&iacute;a Nam v&agrave; T&acirc;y Nam c&oacute; d&atilde;y n&uacute;i Voi (1.754 m) v&agrave; Y&agrave;ng Sreng bao bc.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '15:43:30', 1, 'admin');
