 &atilde;  ra c&ocirc;ng vic lp ao. Ngi Vit th&igrave; quen gi &oacute; l&agrave; B&ugrave;ng binh Ch Bn Th&agrave;nh cho d&ugrave; t&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh thc &atilde; tng i l&agrave; "C&ocirc;ng trng Cng H&ograve;a", "C&ocirc;ng trng Di&ecirc;n Hng", ri "Qung trng Qu&aacute;ch Th Trang". Mt bc ch l&agrave; Rue d''Espagne, ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng l&agrave; rue Vi&eacute;not, v&agrave; ph&iacute;a t&acirc;y l&agrave; rue Schroeder. Nm 1955 thi  nht Cng h&ograve;a Vit Nam, bn con ng n&agrave;y i t&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh ng L&ecirc; Th&aacute;nh T&ocirc;n, ng Phan Bi Ch&acirc;u v&agrave; ng Phan Ch&acirc;u Trinh.<br /><br />Ng&ocirc;i ch mi do h&atilde;ng thu Brossard et Maupin khi c&ocirc;ng x&acirc;y dng t nm 1912 n cui th&aacute;ng 3 nm 1914 th&igrave; ho&agrave;n tt. L n mng ch kh&aacute;nh th&agrave;nh c b&aacute;o ch&iacute; thi &oacute; gi l&agrave; "T&acirc;n Vng Hi", do c din ra trong ba ng&agrave;y 28, 29 v&agrave; 30 th&aacute;ng 3 nm 1914, vi ph&aacute;o b&ocirc;ng, xe hoa v&agrave; hn 100.000 ngi tham d, k c t c&aacute;c tnh  v.<br /><br />Khu ch mi n&agrave;y vn mang t&ecirc;n gi Bn Th&agrave;nh; tuy nhi&ecirc;n cho n trc nm 1975 t&ecirc;n gi ch Bn Th&agrave;nh n&agrave;y thng ch hin din trong s&aacute;ch v, c&ograve;n ngi d&acirc;n th&igrave; thng gi l&agrave; ch S&agrave;i G&ograve;n hay ch Mi,  ph&acirc;n bit ch C ti im c, vn ch c&ograve;n li gian h&agrave;ng tht. Phn c&ograve;n li b ph&aacute; i v&agrave; c ngi Ph&aacute;p x&acirc;y dng th&agrave;nh c quan Ng&acirc;n kh. Hai con ng b&ecirc;n h&ocirc;ng ch m&atilde;i n nm 1940 c&ograve;n l&agrave; bn xe &ograve; min &ocirc;ng v&agrave; min T&acirc;y. V sau, bn xe n&agrave;y mi c di i ch kh&aacute;c.<br /><br />Ch Bn Th&agrave;nh hot ng li&ecirc;n tc trong 70 nm. T ng&agrave;y 1 th&aacute;ng 7 n 15 th&aacute;ng 8 nm 1985, ch Bn Th&agrave;nh c ci to v&agrave; sa cha ln.<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * a ch: Ca Nam (nm gia c&aacute;c ng Phan Bi Ch&acirc;u - Phan Chu Trinh - L&ecirc; Th&aacute;nh T&ocirc;n - C&ocirc;ng trng Qu&aacute;ch Th Trang) - Phng Bn Th&agrave;nh - Qun 1<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * in thoi: +84.8.8292096<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Din t&iacute;ch: 13.056 m&sup2;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Ng&agrave;nh h&agrave;ng kinh doanh ch yu: Qun &aacute;o, vi si, giy d&eacute;p, thi trang, h&agrave;ng th c&ocirc;ng m ngh, thc phm ti sng, tr&aacute;i c&acirc;y, hoa ti.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce021481af_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Ch Bn Th&agrave;nh<br /></em></p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '18:24:41', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (123, 3, 4, 'Hoan Kiem Lake', '', 'hoan-kiem-lake', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Hoan Kiem Lake</strong> (Vietnamese: H Ho&agrave;n Kim, meaning "Lake of the Returned Sword" or "Lake of the Restored Sword", also known as H Gm - Sword Lake) is a lake in the historical center of Hanoi, the capital city of Vietnam. The lake is one of the major scenic spots in the city and serves as a focal point for its public life.</p>', '<h2>History</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">According to the legend, emperor L&ecirc; Li handed a magic sword called Heaven''s Will which brought him victory in his revolt against the Chinese Ming Dynasty back to the Golden Turtle God (Kim Qui) in the lake and hence gave it its present name (the lake was formerly known as "Luc Thuy" meaning "Green Water"). The Tortoise Tower (Thap R&ugrave;a) standing on a small island near the center of lake is linked to the legend.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7c880db619c_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Turtle Tower</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Large soft-shell turtles, either of the species Rafetus swinhoei or a separate species named Rafetus leloii in honor of the emperor, have been sighted in the lake. The species is critically endangered and the number of individuals in the lake is unclear.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7c880ed46f3_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>The Huc Bridge</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />Near the northern shore of the lake lies Jade Island on which the Ngoc Son Temple (Jade Mountain Temple) stands. The temple was erected in the 18th century. It honors the 13-century military leader Tran Hung Dao who distinguished himself in the fight against the Yuan Dynasty, Van Xuong, a scholar, and Nguyen Van Sieu, a Confucian master and famous writer in charge of repairs made to the temple in 1864. Jade Island is connected to the shore by the wooden red-painted Huc Bridge (The Huc, meaning Morning Sunlight Bridge).</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '18:25:43', 1, 'admin');
INSERT INTO news_article_revision (revision_id, article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name) VALUES (124, 4, 14, 'H Hon Kim', '', 'ho-hoan-kiem', '<p>H Ho&agrave;n Kim hay h Gm l&agrave; mt h nc ngt nm gia th &ocirc; H&agrave; Ni. T&ecirc;n h cng c t cho mt qun ca H&agrave; Ni, qun Ho&agrave;n Kim.</p>', '<h2><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px;">C&aacute;ch &acirc;y khong 6 th k, h Gm gm hai phn chy d&agrave;i t ph H&agrave;ng &agrave;o, qua Hai B&agrave; Trng, L&yacute; Thng Kit ti ph H&agrave;ng Chui, th&ocirc;ng vi s&ocirc;ng Hng. Nc h quanh nm xanh bic n&ecirc;n h Gm cng c gi l&agrave; h Lc Thu.</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />Tng truyn v&agrave;o th k 15 h c i t&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh h Ho&agrave;n Kim, gn lin vi truyn thuyt tr gm thn cho R&ugrave;a V&agrave;ng, ghi li thng li ca cuc chin u 10 nm ca nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n Vit Nam chng li qu&acirc;n Minh (1417-1427) di s l&atilde;nh o ca L&ecirc; Li. Truyn thuyt k rng khi L&ecirc; Li khi ngha  Lam Sn (Thanh Ho&aacute;) c&oacute; m&ograve; c mt li gm, sau &oacute; li nht c mt c&aacute;i chu&ocirc;i  rung c&agrave;y, gh&eacute;p li th&agrave;nh thanh gm, t t&ecirc;n l&agrave; Thun Thi&ecirc;n. Gm b&aacute;u n&agrave;y &atilde; theo L&ecirc; Li trong sut thi gian kh&aacute;ng chin chng gic Minh. Khi l&ecirc;n ng&ocirc;i v &oacute;ng &ocirc;  Thng Long, trong mt ln nh&agrave; vua i chi thuyn tr&ecirc;n h Lc Thu, bng mt con r&ugrave;a xut hin. L&ecirc; Th&aacute;i T r&uacute;t gm khi v, gi gm ra th&igrave; gm bay v ph&iacute;a con r&ugrave;a. R&ugrave;a ngm gm, ln xung &aacute;y h, v&agrave; t &oacute; h Lc Thu c&oacute; t&ecirc;n gi mi l&agrave; h Ho&agrave;n Kim (tr gm) hay h Gm.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7c880db619c_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>H Ho&agrave;n Kim vi Th&aacute;p R&ugrave;a</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 10px;">H Ho&agrave;n Kim c du kh&aacute;ch cho l&agrave; mt thng cnh ca H&agrave; Ni. Quanh h trng nhiu loi hoa v&agrave; c&acirc;y cnh. Gia h c&oacute; th&aacute;p R&ugrave;a, cnh h c&oacute; n Ngc Sn. Xung quanh h c&ograve;n c&oacute; nhng di t&iacute;ch lch s kh&aacute;c nh tng vua L&ecirc; Th&aacute;i T, cu Th&ecirc; H&uacute;c, th&aacute;p B&uacute;t, n B&agrave; Kiu,... b&ecirc;n cnh nhng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh kin tr&uacute;c hin i. To&agrave; nh&agrave; Bu in vi th&aacute;p ng h c k&iacute;nh in b&oacute;ng h Gm &atilde; i v&agrave;o l&ograve;ng nhiu ngi d&acirc;n H&agrave; Ni.</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://phuocnh/tomatocms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7c8c8a03f71_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Cu Th&ecirc; H&uacute;c dn v&agrave;o n Ngc Sn</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ngi d&acirc;n H&agrave; Ni sng  khu vc quanh h c&oacute; th&oacute;i quen ra &acirc;y tp th dc v&agrave;o s&aacute;ng sm, c bit l&agrave; v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a h&egrave;. H gi c&aacute;c khu ph nm quanh h l&agrave; B H.<br /><br />Th&aacute;p B&uacute;t (hay l&agrave; b&uacute;t th&aacute;p) nm  cnh h, i vi &agrave;i nghi&ecirc;n nm  b h. Mi ng&agrave;y, b&oacute;ng ca Th&aacute;p b&uacute;t ng xung chm mc trong &agrave;i nghi&ecirc;n, to th&agrave;nh mt biu tng rt p cho hc vn: "Th&aacute;p B&uacute;t - &agrave;i nghi&ecirc;n -  th l&ecirc;n tri xanh"<br /><br />Chu vi s&aacute;t b h l&agrave; khong 1750m, c&ograve;n chu vi ng xe c gii i v&ograve;ng quanh h l&agrave; khong 2000m.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', '18:26:00', 1, 'admin');


